  <brief_title>An Observational Study of IgA Nephropathy: Pathological Variants and Clinical Data</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Observational Study of the Relationship Between Pathological Variants and Clinical Data at Presentation and Follow-up in IgA Nephropathy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
